                <p><em>Reference: DOCKER_KUBERNETES_MIGRATION_STRATEGY.tt (Phases 3-6), PRODUCTION_DB_KUBERNETES_MIGRATION_PLAN.tt (Grok)</em></p>
                <p><strong>Critical Notes</strong>:</p>
                <ul style="font-size: 0.9em;">
                    <li>All IP addresses are examples - substitute your actual network configuration</li>
                    <li>Test entire procedure in staging environment first</li>
                    <li>Maintain bare-metal database for minimum 3 days post-cutover</li>
                    <li>Monitor Galera cluster health continuously during migration</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
